text: Nandrolone cyclohexanecarboxylate (brand names Nor-Durandron, Norlongandron; former developmental code name NSC-3351), or nandrolone hexahydrobenzoate, also known as 19-nortestosterone 17β-cyclohexanecarboxylate, is a synthetic androgen and anabolic steroid and a nandrolone ester that has been marketed by Ferring Pharmaceuticals since at least 1961. ==See also== * List of androgen esters § Nandrolone esters ==References== Category:Androgens and anabolic steroids Category:Cyclohexanes Category:Estranes Category:Nandrolone esters Category:Prodrugs Category:Progestogens Category:Testosterone
title: Nandrolone cyclohexanecarboxylate
